sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant OpenMeow
  participant SDK as @openclaw/sdk
  participant Gateway
  participant Agent
  OpenMeow->>SDK: session.send(prompt)
  SDK->>Gateway: sessions.send / agent
  Gateway->>Agent: enqueue run
  Agent-->>Gateway: events
  Gateway-->>SDK: raw events
  SDK-->>OpenMeow: normalized events
  OpenMeow->>SDK: run.wait() / cancel()
